      <title>美元本月表现糟糕，但对其他主要货币来说却是利好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/dollar-s-terrible-month-is-boon-for-major-currencies-elsewhere</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储即将降息，这让本月美元遭受重创，导致这一世界储备货币大幅下跌，并引发全球主要货币的上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/dollar-s-terrible-month-is-boon-for-major-currencies-elsewhere</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 13:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁安巴尼宣称清洁能源是新的增长引擎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/billionaire-ambani-touts-clean-energy-as-new-growth-engine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[信实工业有限公司董事长穆克什·安巴尼表示，信实工业有限公司新兴的清洁能源业务有望在七年内达到如今石油化工业务的规模。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/billionaire-ambani-touts-clean-energy-as-new-growth-engine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 13:13:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃尔玛和道明证券交易推动美国股票销售量创 5 月以来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/walmart-td-deals-boost-us-share-sale-volume-to-highest-since-may</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃尔玛公司以 36 亿美元退出中国京东公司，使得 8 月成为自 5 月份以来美国上市公司新股和现有股票出售最繁忙的一个月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/walmart-td-deals-boost-us-share-sale-volume-to-highest-since-may</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 13:09:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>强劲数据表明美联储采取谨慎措施，美国国债收益率上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/treasury-yields-rise-after-resilient-data-suggests-measured-fed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在强劲的经济报告促使交易员略微下调对美联储今年宽松政策范围的预期后，美国国债收益率小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/treasury-yields-rise-after-resilient-data-suggests-measured-fed</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 13:07:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
